[{'action': 'opened', 'author': 'em92', 'comment_id': None, 'datetime': '2019-08-21 05:37:05+00:00', 'masked_author': 'username_0', 'text': "Let's have scenario. We have feed with discount (example https://feed.eugenemolotov.ru/?action=display&bridge=Steam&userid=76561198260599288&only_discount=on&format=Atom )

So time ago, there was a discount. My rss reader fetched item from feed. This item's id is `http://store.steampowered.com/app/519860/`. Some time later, Steam stopped giving discounts. Ok.

Then, when discount appears again, there will be item in feed. But it will have the same id, and IMHO it won't appear again in my rss reader (at least as new item).

@username_1 as you are bridge maintainer, any comments?", 'title': '[SteamBridge] Question about items', 'type': 'issue'}
